data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This stunning property sits on a spacious 2.2-acre lot, offering you the perfect blend of tranquility and convenience. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this residence spans 2607 SqFt, providing ample space for comfortable living. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a thoughtfully designed interior featuring modern finishes and a warm, inviting atmosphere. The layout seamlessly connects the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an ideal space for entertaining friends and family. One of the standout features of this home is its breathtaking views of the sunsets and mountains. Imagine unwinding on your patio or gazing out from the large windows as the sun dips below the horizon, casting vibrant hues across the landscape. The spacious bedrooms offer a peaceful retreat, and the well-appointed bathrooms add a touch of luxury to your daily routine. Located in a private gated community you'll have easy access to local amenities. Call for a tour today!
